        <text>
            <body>
                <p>
                <persName key="stutzmann_himanis#324654" xml:id="d1e144465" corresp="Humbert de Baugé, évêque d'Autun (1140 -1148)">Humbertus, Dei gratia
                        <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#319548" xml:id="d1e144467" corresp="Autun (Saône-et-Loire, Autun)">Eduensis</placeName> episcopus</persName>, dilecto sibi in Christo fratri
                    <persName key="stutzmann_himanis#324659" corresp="Guillaume I d’Epiry, abbé de Fontenay (1126-1154)">
                    <app>
                        <lem>Willermo</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#D">Guillelmo</rdg>
                    </app> abbati <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e144478" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Fontenay (1119 -)">Fonteneti</orgName>
                </persName> ejusque successoribus in perpetuum regulariter substituendis. Postulasti
                dilecte in Domino frater totaque <app>
                    <lem>
                        <app>
                            <lem>per</lem>
                            <rdg wit="#D">pro</rdg>
                        </app> te cui prees</lem>
                    <rdg type="omis" wit="#a" />
                </app> congregatio <app>
                    <lem>quatinus</lem>
                    <rdg wit="#D #a">quatenus</rdg>
                </app> dona et concessiones vel alias <app>
                    <lem>adquisitiones</lem>
                    <rdg wit="#D">aqquisitiones</rdg>
                    <rdg>acquisitiones</rdg>
                </app>ecclesie cui Deo <app>
                    <lem>actore</lem>
                    <rdg wit="#D">auctore</rdg>
                    <rdg wit="#a">autore</rdg>
                </app> presides factas decreti nostri sigillato privilegio confirmaremus quatenus
                firmiori ea munimine in perpetuum eadem ecclesia possideret. Quia igitur dignum est
                justis postulationibus assensum prebere sicut bone memorie predecessorem nostrum <app>
                    <lem>domnum</lem>
                    <rdg wit="#D #a">dominum</rdg>
                </app>
                <persName key="stutzmann_himanis#324643" xml:id="d1e144519" corresp="Étienne Ier de Baugé, évêque d'Autun (1112 -1139)">Stephanum
                    episcopum</persName> fecisse cognovimus, nos quoque <app>
                    <lem>sub</lem>
                    <rdg wit="#D">subter</rdg>
                </app> sancte Eduensis ecclesie tutela et protectione monasterium ipsum quod <app>
                    <lem>Dei dispensatione regis</lem>
                    <rdg wit="#a">Dei et regis dispensatione</rdg>
                </app> suscipimus et presentis scripti patrocinio communimus, statuentes ut
                quecumque bona seu possessiones in presentiarum idem monasterium in nostro
                episcopatu possidet sive in futurum possessurum est, firma ei illibataque in
                perpetuum permaneant. <app>
                    <lem>
                        <witEnd wit="#a" />
                        <witDetail wit="#a">Suite jusqu'à "Amen" remplacée par "(on détaille les
                            biens confirmés)"</witDetail>
                    </lem>
                </app>
                <app>
                    <lem>Nominatimque</lem>
                    <rdg wit="#D">Nominati</rdg>
                </app> prefati predecessoris nostri dona et Eduensis capituli assensum et
                concessionem illorum donorum predicto monasterio confirmamus, dona scilicet vallis
                in qua jamdictum monasterium sedet, donum loci <persName key="stutzmann_himanis#325467" corresp="Martinus heremita (ca. 1117)">
                    <app>
                        <lem>domni</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#D">domini</rdg>
                    </app> Martini heremite</persName> cum omnibus appenditiis suis, donum grangie
                    <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324911" xml:id="d1e144556" corresp="Grand-Jailly (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">
                    <app>
                        <lem>Jailiaci</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#D">Jaliaci</rdg>
                    </app>
                </placeName> seu <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#325165" xml:id="d1e144563" corresp="Carmeti">Carmeti</placeName> cum omnibus appenditiis suis, donum <app>
                    <lem>terrarum</lem>
                    <rdg wit="#D">tertiarum</rdg>
                </app> grangie <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324451" xml:id="d1e144572" corresp="Flacey (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">Flaciaci</placeName>, donum aasentiarum de <app>
                    <lem>terris</lem>
                    <rdg wit="#D">tertiis</rdg>
                </app> nostris, ut in carta inde scripta et confirmata habetur, donum <app>
                    <lem>adquisitionis</lem>
                    <rdg wit="#D">aqquisitionis</rdg>
                </app>
                <app>
                    <lem>chasamentorum</lem>
                    <rdg wit="#D">casamentorum</rdg>
                </app> nostrorum, donum totius decime omnium possessionum sepedicti monasterii
                ubicumque in nostro episcopatu <app>
                    <lem>sunt</lem>
                    <rdg wit="#D">sint</rdg>
                </app> vel future <app>
                    <lem>sunt</lem>
                    <rdg wit="#D">sint</rdg>
                </app> ad cujuscumque ecclesiarum nostrarum <app>
                    <lem>jus</lem>
                    <rdg wit="#D">vis</rdg>
                </app> antea pertinuerit. Expressiusque de presentibus possessionibus loquentes
                nominamus et confirmamus ecclesie <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e144611" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Fontenay (1119 -)">Fonteneti</orgName> totam decimam grangie <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324479" xml:id="d1e144615" corresp="Éringes (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">
                    <app>
                        <lem>Aringiarum</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#D">Aringiarium</rdg>
                    </app>
                </placeName>, in quocumque sit, sive in nutrimento sive in annona seu in vino sive
                in alio quod decimari soleat, totam similiter decimam grangie <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324911" xml:id="d1e144622" corresp="Grand-Jailly (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">
                    <app>
                        <lem>Jailliaci</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#D">Jaliaci</rdg>
                    </app>
                </placeName> seu <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#325165" xml:id="d1e144629" corresp="Carmeti">Carmeti</placeName>, totam decimam vallis in qua abbatia sedet, totam decimam
                grangie <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#325010" xml:id="d1e144632" corresp="Saint-Agnan (Nièvre, Montsauche)">Sancti
                    Aniani</placeName>, totam decimam grangie <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324451" xml:id="d1e144635" corresp="Flacey (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">Flaciaci</placeName>,
                similiter <app>
                    <lem>ubicumque</lem>
                    <rdg wit="#D">in quocumque</rdg>
                </app> sit. Pro cujus <app>
                    <lem>tamen</lem>
                    <rdg wit="#D">tam</rdg>
                </app> grangie decima quia <persName key="stutzmann_himanis#326056" corresp="Gérard, prêtre de Seigny (fl. 1142)">Girardus quidam <app>
                        <lem>tunc</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#D">te</rdg>
                    </app>
                    <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324356" xml:id="d1e144658" corresp="Seigny (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">
                        <app>
                            <lem>Saigniaci</lem>
                            <rdg wit="#D">Sanhiaci</rdg>
                        </app>
                    </placeName>
                    <app>
                        <lem>presbiter</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#D">postulabit</rdg>
                    </app>
                </persName>, in cujus <app>
                    <lem>parrochia</lem>
                    <rdg wit="#D">parochia</rdg>
                </app> pars territorii grangie <app>
                    <lem>est</lem>
                    <rdg wit="#D">e</rdg>
                </app>, querelam licet injuste commoverat — nam <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e144682" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Fontenay (1119 -)">Fontenetensis</orgName>
                ecclesia habet de omni decima sua privilegium et domini pape Innocentii cum universo
                    <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#281483" xml:id="d1e144685" corresp="ordre des cisterciens">ordine
                    Cisterciensi</orgName> et sepedicti predecessoris nostri cum laude et assensu
                conventus <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#281272" xml:id="d1e144689" corresp="évêché d'Autun">Eduensium
                    canonicorum</orgName> — nos tamen providentes utriusque ecclesie perpetue paci <app>
                    <lem>quia</lem>
                    <rdg wit="#D">cum</rdg>
                </app> utraque ecclesia nostra <app>
                    <lem>est</lem>
                    <rdg wit="#D">ea</rdg>
                </app>, acceptum missale a <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e144704" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Fontenay (1119 -)">Fontenetensi</orgName> ecclesia dedimus ecclesie <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324356" xml:id="d1e144707" corresp="Seigny (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">
                    <app>
                        <lem>Saigniaci</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#D">Sanhiaci</rdg>
                    </app>
                </placeName> et decimam jamdictam, laudante predicto <persName key="stutzmann_himanis#326056" corresp="Gérard, prêtre de Seigny (fl. 1142)">Girardo</persName> confirmavimus ecclesie <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e144718" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Fontenay (1119 -)">Fonteneti</orgName>. </p>
                <p>Affuerunt rei huic<app>
                    <lem type="nihil" />
                    <rdg wit="#D">rei</rdg>
                </app>
                <app>
                    <lem>domnus</lem>
                    <rdg wit="#D">dominus</rdg>
                </app>
                <persName key="stutzmann_himanis#325478" corresp="Constantin, abbé d'Oigny (fl. 1142)">Constantinus <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#283960" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame, Saint-Laurent et Saint-Nicolas d'Oigny (1106 -)"><app>
                            <lem>Ungiacensis</lem>
                            <rdg wit="#D">Ongiacensis</rdg>
                        </app></orgName> abbas</persName>, dominus <persName key="stutzmann_himanis#324650" corresp="Geoffroy, archidiacre dans le diocèse d'Autun">
                    <app>
                        <lem>Gaufridus</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#D">Gautridus</rdg>
                    </app> archidiaconus noster</persName>, <persName key="stutzmann_himanis#326058" corresp="Arnaud, doyen du chapitre de Saulieu (fl. 1142)">Arnoldus <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#281101" corresp="église Saint-Andoche de Saulieu">Sedelocensium canonicorum</orgName> decanus</persName>, <persName key="stutzmann_himanis#326063" corresp="Hermuinus, archiprêtre (fl. 1142)">Hermuinus <app>
                        <lem>archipresbiter</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#D">archipresbyter</rdg>
                    </app>
                </persName>, <persName key="stutzmann_himanis#326060" corresp="Aimon, chanoine de Saulieu (fl. 1142)">Haymo canonicus <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#283960" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame, Saint-Laurent et Saint-Nicolas d'Oigny (1106 -)"><app>
                            <lem>Ungiacensis</lem>
                            <rdg wit="#D">Ongiacensis</rdg>
                        </app></orgName>
                </persName>.</p>
                <p>De quadam etiam <app>
                    <lem>terra</lem>
                    <rdg wit="#D">tercia</rdg>
                </app> quam <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e144777" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Fontenay (1119 -)">Fontenetenses</orgName> de elemosina predecessoris nostri <app>
                    <lem>esse</lem>
                    <rdg wit="#D">ea</rdg>
                </app> dicebant, sed <persName key="stutzmann_himanis#326056" corresp="Gérard, prêtre de Seigny (fl. 1142)">
                    <app>
                        <lem>Girardus</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#D">
                            <sic>Girard</sic>
                        </rdg>
                    </app>
                </persName> de patrimonio eclesie<placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324356" xml:id="d1e144795" corresp="Seigny (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">
                    <app>
                        <lem>Saigniaci</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#D">Sanhiaci</rdg>
                    </app>
                </placeName>
                <app>
                    <lem>esse</lem>
                    <rdg wit="#D">se</rdg>
                </app> reclamabat, hanc fecimus concordiam quod <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e144808" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Fontenay (1119 -)">Fontenetenses</orgName>
                <app>
                    <lem>dederunt</lem>
                    <rdg wit="#D">dederint</rdg>
                </app> ecclesie <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324356" xml:id="d1e144816" corresp="Seigny (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">
                    <app>
                        <lem>Saigniaci</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#D">Sanhiaci</rdg>
                    </app>
                </placeName>
                <term>librum qui apellatur agende</term>
                <note> Livre contenant l’office des morts. « Agende » est au féminin pluriel pour
                    « laudes ».</note>. Et nos, laudante <persName key="stutzmann_himanis#326056" corresp="Gérard, prêtre de Seigny (fl. 1142)">Girardo</persName>, <app>
                    <lem>terram</lem>
                    <rdg wit="#D">tertiam</rdg>
                </app> illam ecclesie <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e144837" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Fontenay (1119 -)">Fonteneti</orgName> concessimus sicut eam a predecessore nostro se accepisse
                cum aliis <app>
                    <lem>terris</lem>
                    <rdg wit="#D">tertiis</rdg>
                </app>
                <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324451" xml:id="d1e144845" corresp="Flacey (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">Flaciaci</placeName>
                <app>
                    <lem>dicebant</lem>
                    <rdg wit="#D">dicebat</rdg>
                </app>. Actum est<note> est hoc <hi rend="italic">D</hi>.</note>
                <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#319548" xml:id="d1e144858" corresp="Autun (Saône-et-Loire, Autun)">Edue</placeName> in
                domo nostra presentibus archidiaconibus nostris <persName key="stutzmann_himanis#324650" corresp="Geoffroy, archidiacre dans le diocèse d'Autun">
                    <app>
                        <lem>Gaufrido</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#D">Gaulhido</rdg>
                    </app>
                </persName> et <persName key="stutzmann_himanis#324651" corresp="Seguin, archidiacre dans le diocèse d'Autun">Siguino</persName> et
                multis aliis. Decernimus ergo ut prefatas ecclesie <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e144872" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Fontenay (1119 -)">Fonteneti</orgName>
                possessiones, et si que sunt alie a quibuscumque collate vel in futurum conferende,
                nulli liceat vel minuere vel auferre vel ademptas retinere vel injustis vexationibus
                ecclesiam pro eis fatigare. Quod si qua <app>
                    <lem>vel</lem>
                    <rdg wit="#D">ut</rdg>
                </app> ecclesiastica secularisve persona <app>
                    <lem>scienter</lem>
                    <rdg wit="#D">scientes</rdg>
                </app> contra hanc decreti nostri censuram et <app>
                    <lem wit="#B #D-corr">appositi</lem>
                    <rdg wit="#D">
                        <del>apostolici</del>
                        <add place="margin">apositi</add>
                    </rdg>
                </app> sigilli reverentiam facere presumpserit, <app>
                    <lem>actoritate</lem>
                    <rdg wit="#D">auctoritate</rdg>
                </app> Dei et nostra qua fungimur a sacratissimo corpore et sanguine Domini et ab
                ejus ecclesia eum excommunicamus et in perpetuum nisi resipiscat eadem
                excommunicatione a <app>
                    <lem wit="D-post-corr">consortio justorum</lem>
                </app> separamus. Pax sit custodientibus eam. Amen. </p>
                <p>
                <app>
                    <lem>
                        <witStart wit="#a" />
                    </lem>
                </app>Confirmationi huic <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#319548" xml:id="d1e144912" corresp="Autun (Saône-et-Loire, Autun)">Edue</placeName> in <app>
                    <lem>synodo</lem>
                    <rdg wit="#D">sinodo</rdg>
                </app>
                <app>
                    <lem>acte</lem>
                    <rdg wit="#a">acta</rdg>
                </app>, anno ab incarnatione Domini <app>
                    <lem>
                        <num>m° c xl° ii°</num>
                    </lem>
                    <rdg wit="#D">millesimo centesimo quadragesimo secundo</rdg>
                </app>
                <app>
                    <lem>
                        <witEnd wit="#a" />
                    </lem>
                </app>, <app>
                    <lem>
                        <num>vi°</num>
                    </lem>
                    <rdg wit="#D">sexto</rdg>
                </app> idus Novembris, affuerunt et laudaverunt archidiaconi nostri <persName key="stutzmann_himanis#324650" corresp="Geoffroy, archidiacre dans le diocèse d'Autun">
                    <app>
                        <lem>Gaufridus</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#D">Gautridus</rdg>
                    </app>
                </persName>, <persName key="stutzmann_himanis#324588" xml:id="d1e144951" corresp="Henri de Bourgogne, évêque d'Autun (1148 -1171)">Henricus
                    filius ducis</persName> et <persName key="stutzmann_himanis#325488" corresp="Humbert, archidiacre dans le diocèse d'Autun">Humbertus</persName>.</p>
            </body>
        </text>
